import React from 'react';
import {Text, View, Image, TextInput, TouchableOpacity, Button, openImagePicker} from 'react-native';
import { FontAwesome, AntDesign } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import styles from '../Styles/StylesAnunciar';

export default function Anunciar() {
  return (
  <View style={styles.container}>
      <View style={styles.ViewTop}>
        <TouchableOpacity style={styles.botaoRetorno}>
          <AntDesign name="back" size={24} color="black" />
        </TouchableOpacity>
        <Image>
        </Image>
        <View style={{ flex: 1, alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
        <Button title="Select Image" onPress={openImagePicker} />
        {Image && <Image source={{ uri: `data:image/png;base64,${Image}` }}/>}
        </View>
      </View>
        <View style={styles.viewCentral}>
          <TextInput style={styles.textInput}>
          </TextInput>
          <TextInput style={styles.textInput}>
          </TextInput>
          <TextInput style={styles.textInput}>
          </TextInput>
          <TextInput style={styles.textInput}>
          </TextInput>
        </View>
      <View style={styles.viewFinal}>
        <TouchableOpacity>
          <Text>Anunciar</Text>
        </TouchableOpacity>
      </View>
  </View>
  );
}
